1970;;El Condor;;American;;John Guillermin;;Jim Brown, Lee Van Cleef;;western;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/El_Condor_(film);;Luke, an escaped convict, and Jaroo, a loner gold prospector, team up with a band of Apache Indians in 19th century Mexico to capture a large, heavily armed fortress for the millions—or billions—of dollars in gold that are rumored to be stored within.